{"tid":751302,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股神渾水認為毛記（1716）3蚊以下買得過！","createTime":"2018-07-21T17:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T12:32:48.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fdac287e1b737364c2cf81035f08ba640fe2b424","tid":751302,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"渾水認為，毛記的業務性質與Hypebeast（8359）的相近，同樣講求「食腦」有創意，而Hypebeast過去1年多的業績持續改善，股價也持續上揚，因此相信只要毛記管理層能夠持續推出新搞作，多舉辦如《東方昇特異功能救香港》的表演，自然能加強盈利能力、推高估值，故此當毛記見3元水平時，他會積極考慮買一注毛記股票，「押注3位『腦細』將來成功」。Hypebeast最近一期業績的年化純利為5,614萬元，以今日收市價0.85元計，對應的市盈率為30.3倍，遠低於毛記的市盈率。"},{"pid":"2f346a75421d41bb7c8a7dd2f3c78a2375d3f3ad","tid":751302,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:57:24.000Z","msg":"蓋清咁勤力，咁夜仲開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5807ff87d3ec48ee0256ac1af774d895770fdc19","tid":751302,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"CK單野搞到咁大獲 觀望住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1d551470e59b4bac988c9cdf0bc17c86225e5f","tid":751302,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5807ff87d3ec48ee0256ac1af774d895770fdc19","tid":751302,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"CK單野搞到咁大獲 觀望住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:10:16.000Z","msg":"煲水新聞"},{"pid":"cd8f44c12a99916b316f25f59854e05576dccb84","tid":751302,"uid":14144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1d551470e59b4bac988c9cdf0bc17c86225e5f","tid":751302,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5807ff87d3ec48ee0256ac1af774d895770fdc19","tid":751302,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"CK單野搞到咁大獲 觀望住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},